column4:
Dear, 

As-salamu alaykum,

My name is Zaki Shaibu the procurement officer PA under the 
ministry of foreign affair in the UAE under the currect minister 
H.H. Sheikh Abdullah bin Zayed.

We need your quotation on the attached order and your urgent 
response will me appreciated.

Regards,
Zaki Shaibu
Ministry Of foreign Affairs,
Dubai,
UAE.
